description: Wallenstam AB builds, develops, and buys properties in metropolitan areas. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 252 full-time employees.  The Company’s primary activity is the acquisition, management and development of both residential and non-residential real estate located in the Stockholm, Gothenburg and Helsingborg areas in Sweden. The firm primarily manages and develops residential properties, as well as offices, shops, industrial buildings and warehouses, among others. Additionally, the Company is engaged in the supply of electricity to its customers by means of its own wind turbines and hydro power. The firm is active through a number of directly and indirectly owned subsidiaries.
